                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Londo wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">You stole my name.  By the laws of the Couro Prido, I challenge you to the Morago, Llondo Mollari!</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
